author: Shaun M
title: Migos Feat. 2 Chainz "Deadz" Video
text:
Posted by Shaun M , Feb 23, 2017 at 12:47pm Subscribe to HNHH TV Migos and 2 Chainz connect in the blinged out video for "Deadz." 
Migos spilled a lot of ink this week. On Thursday, the Sean Kingston -stompers released the video for "Deadz" -- the latest single off their album Culture -- featuring perennial ATL star 2 Chainz . 
The video starts out with an orchestra playing the instrumentals. Quavo shows up, iced-out, in an upscale and immaculate mansion like it's a Sunday afternoon after the turn up. The trio then flex in a funeral parlor, using wads of cash for folding hand fans. They count their money over dead presidents -- and Ben Franklin -- lying in their fresh coffins. 
2 Chainz and Migos then stunt on a monument while the orchestra plays below. Takeoff and Offset round out the song as zombie presidents wake up.
